snippet.title: Rhapsody: Marl Kingdom Chronicles - Rhapsody II Spotlight Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Rhapsody: Marl Kingdom Chronicles is coming to Nintendo Switch on August 29, 2023!

Embark on a musical adventure with Kururu and find true love in Rhapsody II: Ballad of the Little Princess! More songs, a new turn-based battle system, and a charming story await you! 

#MarlKingdomChronicles #NintendoSwitch
